{"tid":124601,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"成日好似企唔穩","createTime":"2017-02-17T17:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T15:48:24.000Z","uid":52247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e92fbea963fbf7aaaf84e46d1c4af5e7c22254b","tid":124601,"uid":52247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"完全係<br />\nI feel the earth move under my feet<br />\n塊地好似唔係平既咁<br />\n企住都想中去其他地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪老"},{"pid":"6caeab8a651512f01a8aa9cf43ce2b390d807623","tid":124601,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"血氣差，有無心悸"},{"pid":"d5331b8dc0d173f468b12cbc67e823d99fd13078","tid":124601,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:26:09.000Z","msg":"耳水不平衡"},{"pid":"6e45cac6d121cb4b2a4bfc256cc95f0ebfa58165","tid":124601,"uid":52247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>血氣差，有無心悸</blockquote><br />\n有但唔多，幾日一次咁"},{"pid":"39ed64c0678461bf6dc7a3c9eaba9f3a33ce5fc7","tid":124601,"uid":36385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"有冇可能係長短腳lol"},{"pid":"14f9105a072241b0adf7d97e49fe7df426b85b2c","tid":124601,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"池內亞也（作者本人）：澤尻英龍華&nbsp;飾<br />\n<br />\n本劇主角，積極活潑的性格令她非常受到身邊的人喜愛。平日有在自己家經營的豆腐店幫忙，屬心地善良和藹可親的好學生，從初中的時候便開始加入學校籃球部，亦喜歡了籃球部的學長。<br />\n在2005年3月，正臨近應考高中入學試的時候，當時15歲的亞也診斷患上脊髓小腦萎縮症，在症狀發展及趨向嚴重期間經歷著各種各樣的事，一面流着眼淚的同時，一面努力面對疾病和命運。在絕望中得到母親潮香的鼓勵，以寫日記（文章）找到自己生存的意義，一直抱着的願望就是能夠幫助他人。最後在25歲時去世。"},{"pid":"a91ab62fd3ae32f828f42a4eb7101f9866ff71fb","tid":124601,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc23ea414e575105bf72f8866d91bf53b4d2fb40","tid":124601,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT